Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.58,0:54:15.58,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? This is part of the Bronze Age.\N{\rChinese}好的？这属于青铜时代的一部分。
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.74,0:54:17.76,English,,0,0,0,,Egypt is the greatest civilization of the Bronze Age.\N{\rChinese}埃及是青铜时代最伟大的文明。
